"The zip extension is missing and unzip/7z commands cannot be called as proc_open is disabled, skipping.\n"
"The zip extension and unzip/7z commands are both missing, skipping.\n"
"<warning>proc_open is disabled so 'unzip' and '7z' commands cannot be used, zip files are being unpacked using the PHP zip extension.</warning>"
"<warning>This may cause invalid reports of corrupted archives. Besides, any UNIX permissions (e.g. executable) defined in the archives will be lost.</warning>"
"<warning>Enabling proc_open and installing 'unzip' or '7z' (21.01+) may remediate them.</warning>"
"<warning>As there is no 'unzip' nor '7z' command installed zip files are being unpacked using the PHP zip extension.</warning>"
"<warning>This may cause invalid reports of corrupted archives. Besides, any UNIX permissions (e.g. executable) defined in the archives will be lost.</warning>"
